      <guid>https://fergul.github.io/project/twitterverse/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Experimented with creating an intuitive abstract visualisation for displaying tweets about a subject using a sun + satellite metaphor. Built as a weekend experiment, using Java and the Twitter API.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Displays a user or hashtag as suns and tweets pop up as moons in real-time, orbiting their topic. Provides users with instant and intuitive visual feedback about how popular a topic is.&lt;/p&gt;



